A vintage-style technical illustration showing two large mechanical gears interlocking and turning in harmony, one gear rendered in warm orange-copper tones representing document pages with spreadsheet grids and presentation slides embossed on its surface, the other gear in deep blue-steel with database forms and structured data patterns etched into its teeth. The gears float against a cream-colored aged paper background with subtle coffee stains and fold marks. Mechanical pencil sketches of connecting rods and pivot points surround the main composition, suggesting an engineer's workshop blueprint. Small oil drops glisten at the contact points where the gears mesh together, conveying smooth integration and synchronized movement.
